name: Suiman
description: SUIMAN is a decentralized cryptocurrency project built on the Sui blockchain. The project aims to create a token ecosystem with a total supply of 1 billion tokens. SUIMAN is designed with zero transaction tax and features a portion of its liquidity pool permanently burned. The project supports trading through major exchanges and can be swapped using $SUI. SUIMAN focuses on simplifying the user experience by providing easy access to the Sui ecosystem for trading and holding $SUIMAN tokens.
